Class BackgroundFactory

java.lang.Object
BackgroundFactory
public class BackgroundFactory
extends java.lang.Object
Factory for asset blocks This stores the indexes of the assets in the csv file: -2 trees, -3 dead trees, -4 wall, -5 newBrickBot1, -6 newBrickBot2, -7 newBrickBot3, -8 flagUp, -9 flagBottom, -10 cage, -11 chainstart, -12 chainmiddle, -13 pot, -14 redFlower, -15 yellowFlower, -16 potdestroyed, -17 chainEnd, -18 windowIron1, -19 windowIron2, -20 windowIron3, -21 tent, -22 fire, -23 Stone , -24 RightArrowSign , -25 DangerSign
